            "Help_1_Title": "Prepare SVG",
            "Help_1_B1": "Each area needs a unique and stable ID.",
            "Help_1_B2": "Use IDs that match the category column.",
            "Help_1_B3": "Avoid duplicate IDs and decorative groups without need.",
            "Help_1_B4": "If you use images, prefer embedded PNG only.",
